dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Mount San Antonio quadrangle, Los Angeles and San Bernardino counties, California
dct_alternative_sm: DF-88 geology Mount San Antinio quadrangle
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from newest available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle MOUNT SAN ANTONIO, CA 1988, NIMA 2452 I SW - Series V895."
"Prepared in cooperation with the Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History and the Angeles National Forest."
Includes 2 col. cross sections, quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
